# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

- Add documentation for drivers
- Fluentd driver for logging
- Live streaming of logs

## [2.0] - 2025-01-11

### Added

- Changelog file
- A new destructored DriverOptions customized for each driver
- PDM support for building and manage dependencies for the project
- Build and deploy on Pipeline

### Changed

- Now, the drivers are more customizable, we changed the DriverOptions to a destructored object. You have as builtin options the following:
  - file
  - stdout
  - graylog

### Added

- Allow DriverOptions imports

### Fixed

- Wrong graylog protocol setter
